skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: swim event chooser
des: This app uses general overall criteria to help users decide what swim events they might prefer. The responses are in "long-course" form so each event is in meters. Each event has a short description that users may ask for with a "tell me more".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
